lead_paragraph: Chris Davis homered to back an effective pitching performance by Yovani Gallardo in his Orioles debut, and Baltimore beat the Minnesota Twins 4-2 Wednesday night at chilly Camden Yards.

headline.print_headline: Davis Homers as Gallardo, Orioles Beat Twins 4-2
